# Drizzle ORM 规范

## 常用操作

```typescript
import { db } from "@/server/db";
import { entities } from "@/server/db/schema";
import { eq, and, desc, asc, isNull, inArray } from "drizzle-orm";

// 查询单条
const [entity] = await db
  .select()
  .from(entities)
  .where(eq(entities.businessId, businessId))
  .limit(1);

// 查询列表
const results = await db
  .select()
  .from(entities)
  .where(and(eq(entities.status, "active"), isNull(entities.parentId)))
  .orderBy(asc(entities.order), desc(entities.createdAt));

// 插入
const [inserted] = await db
  .insert(entities)
  .values({ id: randomUUID(), businessId, title, createdBy: user.id, ... })
  .returning();

// 更新
const [updated] = await db
  .update(entities)
  .set({ title, updatedAt: new Date() })
  .where(eq(entities.businessId, businessId))
  .returning();

// 删除
await db.delete(entities).where(eq(entities.businessId, businessId));
```

## 常用操作符

| 操作符 | 用途 | 示例 |
|--------|------|------|
| `eq` | 等于 | `eq(table.id, value)` |
| `and` | 且 | `and(cond1, cond2)` |
| `or` | 或 | `or(cond1, cond2)` |
| `desc` | 降序 | `orderBy(desc(table.createdAt))` |
| `asc` | 升序 | `orderBy(asc(table.order))` |
| `isNull` | 为空 | `isNull(table.parentId)` |
| `isNotNull` | 不为空 | `isNotNull(table.deletedAt)` |
| `inArray` | 在数组中 | `inArray(table.status, ['a', 'b'])` |
| `like` | 模糊匹配 | `like(table.name, '%keyword%')` |
| `ilike` | 忽略大小写模糊匹配 | `ilike(table.name, '%keyword%')` |

## 禁止事项

- ❌ 使用 Prisma（项目使用 Drizzle ORM）
- ❌ 不使用 `.returning()` 获取插入/更新结果
- ❌ 忘记 `.limit(1)` 查询单条记录
